  "abstract": "The Board of Governors (Board) is publishing a final rule that amends Regulation EE to include additional entities in the definition of \"financial institution\" contained in section 402 of the Federal Deposit Insurance Corporation Improvement Act of 1991 (FDICIA) so that they are covered by FDICIA's netting protections. The final rule also clarifies certain aspects of the existing activities-based test in Regulation EE.",
